<br>
Just wanted to comment about the 4 style evade chain.  While having a 4 style chain is a bit longer than is necessary I regularily use the first 3 moves of the chain.  As a thrust spec'd infiltrator our weapon styles are very weak, and the Gar/AH defense penalty is just too much liability so many infiltrators rely on the evade chain for a large portion of our damage.  This is especially true since epic armor went in and perf chain damage fell through the floor.<br>
<br>
